{"tid":2122420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"721一週年：【聯合聲明：網絡媒體強烈譴責警方無理票控及阻礙傳媒採訪】","createTime":"2020-07-24T03:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T04:19:58.000Z","uid":162969,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfdd7729448ab55423f75bb15357ecdb5fd17064","tid":2122420,"uid":162969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/resistancelive2014/photos/a.1433196946944656/2647607028836969/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fresistancelive2014%2Fphotos%2Fa.1433196946944656%2F2647607028836969%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Ay1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=9b49f4d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/resistancelive2014/photos/a.1433196946944656/2647607028836969/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n多間網媒記者於元朗形點商場、鳳攸北街一帶採訪時，無故遭警方多次截查，更被警方以違反限聚令《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》（《規例》 ）（第599G章）為由而開發告票。警方指網絡媒體並非新聞處承認的傳媒機構而票控多名記者從業員，而擁有記協證或正統主流媒體則可以無條件放行，如斯解釋實屬無稽，更無視記者採訪天職，有違警方應配合傳媒採訪的職責。<br />\n<br />\n連署網媒名單排名不分先後， 名單會陸續更新<br />\n<br />\nCLSHK 知線新聞（香港）<br />\nCLSTW 知線新聞（台灣）<br />\n蛋蛋俱樂部<br />\n荃在感<br />\nResistance live media<br />\n初媒<br />\n實時新聞<br />\n逆天煉成誌<br />\n熙熙直擊-Hei Hei hits<br />\n全民記者<br />\n時代新聞<br />\n幽光媒體<br />\nRagazine<br />\n傑斯頻道<br />\n啤梨晚報<br />\n菜心戰鬥記<br />\n90後社會紀實<br />\n旺角鳩嗚團by Mk Mickey<br />\n自由記者 牧師<br />\n本土新聞<br />\nBooom<br />\nMIHK.tv 香港網絡製造電視<br />\n前線紀錄頻道<br />\n看中國<br />\n眾生絕實<br />\nShutterstock(Newyork)<br />\nscn新聞網<br />\n天天日報<br />\nGuardians of Hong Kong<br />\nBeWater Hk<br />\n拾玖傳媒<br />\n<br />\n2020年7月22日"},{"pid":"3996b91ae71d05a5b50a91291b2235c00c1035ab","tid":2122420,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:50:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f99a67fa8ec0d843d2d3901352a91ab1eadb2b5","tid":2122420,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n食屎啦死黑警"},{"pid":"5654a10f9646dfc2